        {
          "pos": "n",
          "level": 3,
          "en": "The disappointing results of the experiment forced scientists to reconsider assumptions they had long regarded as firmly established.",
          "ko": "실망스러운 실험 결과는 과학자들이 오랫동안 확실하다고 여겨온 가정들을 재고하게 만들었다.",
