          "sort_order": 0
        },
        {
          "pos": "n",
          "level": 2,
          "en": "She set a clear goal before the exam so that she could study more efficiently.",
          "ko": "그녀는 더 효율적으로 공부할 수 있도록 시험 전에 분명한 목표를 세웠다.",
          "sort_order": 1
        },
        {
          "pos": "n",
          "level": 2,
          "en": "The striker scored the winning goal in the final minute of the match.",
          "ko": "그 공격수는 경기 막판에 결승 골을 넣었다.",
          "sort_order": 2
        },
        {
          "pos": "n",
          "level": 3,
          "en": "Psychologists argue that people who write down their long-term goals are more likely to sustain motivation when facing setbacks.",
