        },
        {
          "pos": "a",
          "level": 2,
          "en": "The teacher praised the student whose notes were remarkably neat and well organized.",
          "ko": "선생님은 필기가 놀랄 만큼 깔끔하고 잘 정리된 그 학생을 칭찬했다.",
