          "sort_order": 0
        },
        {
          "pos": "a",
          "level": 2,
          "en": "My grandmother told us many fond memories from the days when she was young.",
          "ko": "할머니는 젊었던 시절의 정겨운 추억들을 우리에게 많이 들려주셨다.",
          "sort_order": 1
        },
        {
          "pos": "a",
          "level": 3,
          "en": "Although he seemed strict in public, colleagues recalled a fond and generous mentor who quietly supported struggling students.",
