        },
        {
          "pos": "v",
          "level": 1,
          "en": "You can exit the room through this door.",
          "ko": "이 문을 통해 방에서 나갈 수 있습니다.",
          "sort_order": 0
        },
        {
          "pos": "v",
          "level": 2,
          "en": "The driver exited the highway because the traffic ahead was completely blocked.",
          "ko": "앞쪽 교통이 완전히 막혀서 운전자는 고속도로를 빠져나갔다.",
          "sort_order": 1
        },
        {
          "pos": "v",
          "level": 3,
          "en": "Investors who exit a volatile market too early often miss the recovery that follows a temporary decline.",
