        {
          "pos": "n",
          "level": 3,
          "en": "His decision to study art was a radical departure from the traditional career path that his family had always expected.",
          "ko": "예술을 공부하겠다는 그의 결정은 가족이 늘 기대해 온 전통적인 진로에서 크게 벗어난 것이었다.",
          "sort_order": 2
        }
      ]
    },
    "2137": {
