        },
        {
          "pos": "n",
          "level": 2,
          "en": "When they reached a fork in the road, they had to decide which way to go.",
          "ko": "그들이 갈림길에 도착했을 때, 어느 쪽으로 갈지 결정해야 했다.",
          "sort_order": 1
